      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total gem. This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014it looks and feels like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' experience without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
