      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe for maximum torsional rigidity. Every component, from the limited-slip differential to the factory-spec dampers, has been meticulously maintained to preserve its original driving dynamics. This is a rare, mechanically impeccable example for the discerning collector who demands absolute performance integrity.",
